  }), mdx("p", null, "Is a degree worth the cost? How do you value a master's degree... or any degree for that matter! "), mdx("p", null, "Are you you asking these same questions? If so, I believe my experience might be useful to you. I just earned my masters's at Western Governor's University."), mdx("p", null, "Over the last several years I've learned managers won't necessarily hire you because you have a master's degree, but they might skip you if you don't. It may not bear on the quality of your work, but it does seem to make getting work easier."), mdx("h2", null, "My Decision to Go Back To School"), mdx("p", null, "It's after eleven on a Friday night. The food at Twin Donut  is cheap and greasy. We're waiting for our food because it's also the only place still open. Sitting at a table, I recount a scene from Good Will Hunting where Matt Damon, as Will, outwits and outsmarts an unoriginal snob in a bar closing with the classic flourish,"), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
